original_title: Konungens af Siam landstigning vid Logårdstrappan
overview: The first Swedish film by photographer Ernest Florman. Kung Oscar II welcomes King Chulalonkorn of Siam, now Thailand, at Logårdstrappan. King Chulalonkorn visited Sweden in connection with Stockholmsutställningen 1897.
title: The Arrival of the King of Siam in Stockholm
